<p>The <b>Arkham Asylum for the Criminally Insane</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Fictional" title="Fictional" class="mw-redirect">fictional</a> setting, a <a href="/wiki/Psychiatric_hospital" title="Psychiatric hospital">psychiatric hospital</a> in the <a href="/wiki/DC_Comics_Universe" title="DC Comics Universe" class="mw-redirect">DC Comics Universe</a>, usually in stories featuring <a href="/wiki/Batman" title="Batman">Batman</a>. Many <a href="/wiki/Psychopath" title="Psychopath" class="mw-redirect">psychopathic</a> criminals, including a number of Batman's enemies, such as <a href="/wiki/Joker_(comics)" title="Joker (comics)">The Joker</a> and <a href="/wiki/Two-Face" title="Two-Face">Two-Face</a>, have been imprisoned within the Asylum.</p>
